(\sin A+\cos A)^2 +(\sin B+\cos B)^2+(\sin C+\cos C)^2=\sin 2A-\sin 2B-\sin 2C-1
A+B+C = 180^\circ
(\sin A+\cos A)^2 +(\sin B+\cos B)^2+(\sin C+\cos C)^2=-4\sin A \cos B \cos C-1
\cos B\cos C
A=90^\circ
\widehat{B}=90^{\circ}-\widehat{C}
\cos\widehat{B}\cos\widehat{C}=\cos\widehat{B}\cos(90^{\circ}-\widehat{B})=\cos\widehat{B}\sin\widehat{B}=\frac{1}{2}\sin(2\widehat{B})
\cos\widehat{B}\cos\widehat{C}\in\left[-\frac{1}{2};\frac{1}{2}\right]
\widehat{B}
